          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The proton,  deuteron and  triton  spectra  from  the",
                " photodisintegration  of Li-6 and Li-6(g,t)He-3 cross",
                " section have been measured. The experimental results",
                " are   confronted   with  the  available  theoretical",
                " predictions.  The deuteron spectrum shows  a  strong",
                " disagreement  with  calculations  performed with and",
                " alfa+d peripheral model. this is also confirmed by a",
                " relatively high cross section of the Li-6(g,He-3)H-3",
                " reaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
